<h4>Origin</h4>
<p>Belief Mapper started out as a final project at <a href="http://devbootcamp.com/">Dev Bootcamp</a> in Chicago on November 26th, 2014. The bulk of the site was built in 8 days by Gina Krieb, Patrick Grenning, Peter Soderberg, and myself. Since then, I have been working on optimizing the site and adding features.</p><br>

<h4>Privacy</h4>
<p>Your personal information is never displayed alongside your beliefs. I also promise never to sell the data collected on this site. This is a not-for-profit personal project.</p><br>

